titleNullable: Target Domains for IAB text/website classification
subtitleNullable: 2.5 Million Target Domains for IAB text/website classification
descriptionNullable:
This is a subset of data from https://front-page.com for testing IAB website classification, a preliminary classification has been attempted and is available in the last column. The counterpart data set is seed-database  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/bpmtips/websiteiabcategorization for training the model which has correct manual categorization.

can also be used for image analysis since the screenshot urls are provided in the dataset.

attribution to https://front-page.com is required.

complete data for 10 million domains available at

https://www.rest-apis.com/
